ZH: 我只能等你回来。
EN: I can only wait for you to come back.

ZH: 他只能去超市买东西。
EN: He can only buy things at the supermarket.

ZH: 我只能跟你保持联系。
EN: I can only keep in touch with you.

ZH: 她只能听朋友的忠告。
EN: She can only listen to her friend's advice.

ZH: 他只能坐公共汽车上班。
EN: He can only take the bus to work.

ZH: 我只能在周末去看电影。
EN: I can only go watch movies on weekends.

ZH: 我只能每天喝一杯咖啡。
EN: I can only drink one cup of coffee per day.

ZH: 他只能每周去健身房两次。
EN: He can only go to the gym twice a week.

ZH: 我只能络绎不绝地工作。
EN: I can only work tirelessly.

ZH: 她只能承受这么多压力。
EN: She can only withstand so much pressure.

ZH: 我只能忍住不哭出来。
EN: I can only hold back my tears.

ZH: 他只能默默地忍受痛苦。
EN: He can only silently endure the pain.

ZH: 我们只能把这个秘密保守。
EN: We can only keep this secret.

ZH: 孩子们只能在外面玩一个小时。
EN: The children can only play outside for one hour.

ZH: 他只能在朋友圈里发照片。
EN: He can only post pictures in his social circle.

ZH: 我只能给你一些建议。
EN: I can only give you some advice.

ZH: 她只能在家里做家务。
EN: She can only do household chores at home.

ZH: 我只能做我力所能及的事情。
EN: I can only do what I am capable of.

ZH: 他只能表示愤怒。
EN: He can only express his anger.

ZH: 我只能接受现实。
EN: I can only accept reality.
